videos.description: Eric Hamilton, Anthony Starzynski and Samson George make their first career starts for Pitt on senior night.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (3 Pitt seniors make their first career starts) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: 3 Pitt seniors make their first career starts

videos.description: Howard Washington slings a nice pass from beyond the arc to Elijah Hughes at the hoop as he lays it in vs. Pitt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cuse's Washington fires long pass to Hughes at the hoop) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Cuse's Washington fires long pass to Hughes at the hoop

videos.description: Joseph Girard pulls up from beyond the arc on two consecutive possessions to extend Syracuse's lead.
videos.headline: Girard drains back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Syracuse's Elijah Hughes uses a series of slick moves to get around his Pitt defender and reach the rim with a finger roll.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hughes hits his defender with a hesitation move for two) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Hughes hits his defender with a hesitation move for two

videos.description: Bourama Sidibe flushes home an alley-oop slam from Marek Dolezaj to keep Syracuse's lead over Pitt big in the second half.
videos.headline: Sidibe completes Cuse alley-oop

videos.description: Brendan Paul pulls up as time expires, draining a 3-pointer as Syracuse caps off a 72-49 win vs. Pitt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Paul's 3 beats the buzzer to cap off Syracuse's big win) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Paul's 3 beats the buzzer to cap off Syracuse's big win
